src:
Sporočilo uredništvom - nadaljevanje seje odbora DZ za obrambo ob 16. uri

07 Nov 2019, 11:22


Ljubljana, 7. novembra - Nadaljevanje seje odbora DZ za obrambo, na kateri bodo razpravljali o nakupu oklepnikov valuk 6x6, bo danes ob 16. uri v sobi 212 DZ na Šubičevi 4, so sporočili iz DZ.
text:
Message to the editorial boards - continuation of the sitting of the National Defense Committee at 4pm

07 Nov 2019, 11:22


Ljubljana, 7 November - The continuation of the session of the National Defense Committee, which will discuss the purchase of 6x6 armored vehicles, will be held today at 4pm in room 212 of the National Assembly on Šubičeva 4, the National Assembly reported.
